quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,64,"Lẹ́yìn náà, ẹ pẹ̀yìndà lẹ́yìn ìyẹn. Tí kì í bá ṣe oore àjùlọ Allāhu àti àánú Rẹ̀ lórí yín, ẹ̀yin ìbá wà nínú ẹni òfò."
  2,65,"Dájúdájú ẹ mọ àwọn tó kọjá ẹnu-ààlà nínú yín nípa ọjọ́ Sabt. A sì sọ fún wọn pé: “Ẹ di ọ̀bọ, ẹni-ìgbéjìnnà sí ìkẹ́ (ẹni àbùkù ẹni yẹpẹrẹ).”"
  2,66,"A sì ṣe é ní ìyà (àríkọ́gbọ́n) fún ẹni tó ṣojú rẹ̀ àti ẹni tó ń bọ̀ lẹ́yìn rẹ̀. (Ó tún jẹ́) wáàsí (ìṣítí) fún àwọn olùbẹ̀rù (Allāhu)."
  3,4,"Tẹ́lẹ̀tẹ́lẹ̀ wọ́n jẹ́ ìmọ̀nà fún àwọn ènìyàn.{1} Ó tún sọ ọ̀rọ̀-ìpínyà (ọ̀rọ̀ tó ń ṣèpínyà láààrin òdodo àti irọ́) kalẹ̀.² Dájúdájú àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú àwọn āyah Allāhu, ìyà tó le ń bẹ fún wọn. Allāhu sì ni Alágbára, Olùgbẹ̀san..",1:[Gbólóhùn yìí níí ṣepọ̀ pẹ̀lú ìjọ àti àsìkò. 2. Fún àlàyé lórí al-Furƙọ̄n, ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Baƙọrah; 2:53.]
  3,5,"Dájúdájú Allāhu, kò sí kiní kan tó pamọ́ fún Un nínú ilẹ̀ àti nínú sánmọ̀."
  3,6,"Òun ni Ẹni tí Ó ń yàwòrán yín sínú àpòlùkẹ́ bí Ó ṣe fẹ́. Kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí a gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àyàfi Òun, Alágbára Ọlọ́gbọ́n."